{"tid":324941,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大熱Kelly「翻版朱千雪」Nicole齊入圍","createTime":"2017-07-16T23:48:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T01:50:51.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b778c5eb1882f918a2bfc736dc0adc6cd3065c0a","tid":324941,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:48:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414442766595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414442766595.jpg&h=3199e9c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nKelly Ng、胡美貽（Nicole）、去年友誼小姐張寶兒的妹妹張寶欣都有入圍。<br />\n<br />\n《2017香港小姐競選》早前經過初選及複選，130多名參加者中選出優秀佳麗入圍競逐，最後入圍的12強終於出爐。「間尺鼻」、「十優港姐」麥明詩的演技班同學仔Zoe、Sophia冇得留低。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414442929592.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414442929592.jpg&h=514423d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAngela、Nicole Kam（TVB圖片）<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414443491266.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414443491266.jpg&h=f9193dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSandy、Suki（TVB圖片）<br />\n12強佳麗包括大熱「青春版李若彤」Kelly Ng、「翻版朱千雪」胡美貽（Nicole）、去年友誼小姐張寶兒的妹妹張寶欣、Nicole Kam、Angela Lau、Juliette、「會計之花」Regina、Sandy Leung、17歲Mandy、Emily Wong、恒管畢業生Katrina、身高1米78的Suki Wong。<br />\n<br />\n其實今屆港姐都算高質，可惜恒管畢業的Josephine、Elsie有樣有身材都未能入圍，外國美女Christina同樣被Foul。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414443671569.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414443671569.jpg&h=4b885243&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nEmily、Regina<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414443897269.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414443897269.jpg&h=52365cd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n17歲Mandy、Katarina<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170704/_2017070414490779982.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170704%2F_2017070414490779982.jpg&h=23261a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n靚女Elsie、「間尺鼻」Moon冇得留低。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/944361/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F944361%2F&d=pGABYCmRHTumhql11H3vy%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0403af34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fent%2F944361%2F&h=d019d161\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/ent/944361/</a>"},{"pid":"7ec367e6f333c68e8a2c61322bf59d0c336ad9b7","tid":324941,"uid":35370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:38:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i65.tinypic.com/2628ifs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi65.tinypic.com%2F2628ifs.png&h=df462f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nN年前cap落嘅圖，冇大圖，得縮圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n收神秘人送嘅大紥花，又收名牌<br />\n不過依家全部刪曬"},{"pid":"fecaf88cf2955f998dbf15a6fc8469ac19c1bb62","tid":324941,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"當中處女沒1個"},{"pid":"05161b35f21ad09a52d591b4bd7f8b1825c9990b","tid":324941,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T01:50:51.000Z","msg":"認真,另一個nicole靚啲"}]}